# ğŸš€ **MY SPACE FPA - COMPLETE TECH STACK & ARCHITECTURE 2026**
## *Enterprise-Grade Full-Stack Solution for Next-Gen Freelance Platform*

---

## **EXECUTIVE SUMMARY**

This document outlines the comprehensive technology stack for building My Space FPA, a feature-rich freelancing platform with real-time collaboration, AI capabilities, video conferencing, IDE integration, and secure payment processing. The stack is chosen for scalability, performance, developer experience, and future-proofing.

