## **PART 1: FRONTEND TECHNOLOGIES**

### **1.1 Web Application (Main Platform)**

| Technology | Version | Purpose | Justification |
|------------|---------|---------|---------------|
| **Next.js** | 15.0.0 | React Framework | App Router, Server Components, SSR, ISR |
| **React** | 19.0.0 | UI Library | Component-based architecture |
| **TypeScript** | 5.4+ | Type Safety | Static typing, better DX |
| **Tailwind CSS** | 4.0 | Styling | Utility-first, responsive |
| **Shadcn/ui** | 2.0 | Component Library | Accessible, customizable |
| **Framer Motion** | 11.0 | Animations | Smooth UI transitions |
| **Zustand** | 5.0 | State Management | Lightweight, scalable |
| **TanStack Query** | 5.0 | Data Fetching | Caching, real-time updates |
| **GraphQL CodeGen** | 5.0 | Type Generation | Type-safe GraphQL |

### **1.2 Mobile Applications**

```javascript
MOBILE_STACK = {
