### **Quick Start Commands**

```bash
# Development
pnpm install
pnpm dev

# Database
docker-compose up -d postgres redis
pnpm prisma migrate dev

# Testing
pnpm test
pnpm test:e2e

# Build
pnpm build
docker build -t my-space-fpa .

# Deploy
kubectl apply -f k8s/
terraform apply
```

